    <section class="membership__description">
        <div class="description__header">
          <h1>Join Us</h1>
          <h2>Become A Member</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="gardens__body no-marge">
            <p>Sign up to become a member and enjoy the freedom of stopping by, 
                mingling with other garden goers, or working in the gardens
                 anytime during hours of operation - free of charge. 
            </p>
  
                <p>A membership also allows you admission to summer events such as concerts, 
                    bbqs, art shows and more. See below for a list of membership benefits.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="membership__description">
        <div class="description__header">
          <h2>Membership Benefits</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="members__list">
